com.hp.hpl.jena.extras.tools.query
Class ModelQuery

java.lang.Object
  com.hp.hpl.jena.extras.tools.query.ModelQuery

public class ModelQuery
extends java.lang.Object

A ModelQuery object holds a collection of (S P O) query triples. Each of the S P O nodes can be an ordinary Model RDFNode or a QueryVariable. When the ModelQuery is run over some Model, it returns a sequence of results; each result (a List) can be supplied to a Queryariable to extract the underlying result binding.

Author:
kers
